casebody.head_matter:
In Re Daniel M. DAVIS, petitioner.
No. 17-7388.
Supreme Court of the United States
Feb. 20, 2018.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for writ of habeas corpus dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
